{{中國的稱謂}}
 
'''大中華'''（英語對應詞：{{lang|en|Greater China}}）是對[[中國|中國]]或[[華人|華人]]概括性的政治、经济及文化概念，主要用於[[學術|學術]]與[[商業|商業]]領域，最早於1930年由[[美國|美國]]地理學家[[葛德石|葛德石]]所提出<ref name="Harding">{{cite journal |first = Harry |last = Harding |title = The Concept of 'Greater China': Themes, Variations and Reservations |journal = The China Quarterly |issue = 136, Special Issue: Greater China |pages = 660 |date = Dec 1993}}</ref>，但實際內涵尚有爭議。通常包含以華人或[[漢文化|漢文化]]為主的[[兩岸四地|兩岸四地]]──[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]、[[香港|香港]]、[[澳門|澳門]]以及[[臺灣|臺灣]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Greater China {{!}} McKinsey & Company|url=https://www.mckinsey.com/cn|accessdate=2020年1月18日|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021年2月3日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203132850/https://www.mckinsey.com/cn|dead-url=no}}</ref>，部份人士認為它還包含[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]及[[泰國|泰國]]的[[華人地區|華人地區]]，也有人認為它包含[[新加坡|新]]、[[馬來西亞|馬]]及[[泰國|泰]]、美洲、歐洲的[[海外華人|海外華人]]社區。「大中華」隱含對包含這些地區的人民屬於[[中華民族|中華民族]]的文化認同，支持者認為可以避免[[兩岸關係|兩岸關係]]中的政治及主權爭議、降低表面上政治與[[意識形態|意識形態]]的衝突。此用詞將[[中華民國|中華民國]]下轄的[[臺澎金馬|臺澎金馬]]與[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]下轄的[[中國内地|中國内地]]、[[港澳地區|港澳地區]]視為同一個框架看待，同時卻不等於指此等地域等同獨立國家。

== 含义 ==
英文「大中華」（{{lang|en|Greater China}}）中的「大」字容易存在其它涵義，除可解作「較大」（{{lang|en|Greater}}）之外，亦可解釋為「廣義」、「泛指」之義。此詞可以從經濟、政治及文化三種意義角度來理解，而分別有大中華經濟圈、大中華政治圈及大中華文化圈。隨著治理、政治、文化、媒體等跨域交流及比較日益增加，各學術領域對「大中華」一詞對全球化、區域化等議題的討論增多。<ref>{{Cite book |publisher = Rowman & Littlefield |isbn = 9780739135341 |last1 = Guo |first1 = Sujian |last2 = Guo |first2 = Baogang |title = Greater China in an Era of Globalization |date = 2010}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |doi = 10.1016/j.tele.2005.12.001 |issn = 0736-5853 |volume = 24 |issue = 1 |pages = 30-40 |last = Yang |first = Kenneth C.C. |title = A comparative study of Internet regulatory policies in the Greater China Region: Emerging regulatory models and issues in China, Hong-Kong SAR, and Taiwan |journal = Telematics and Informatics |accessdate = 2012-11-07 |date = 2007-02 |url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S073658530500064X}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |publisher = Indiana University Press |isbn = 0253220262 |editors = Ying Zhu (ed.) |last1 = Berry |first1 = Christopher |last2 = Chan |first2 = Joseph Man |title = TV China |chapter = Toward TV Regionalization in Greater China and Beyond. TV China: Institutions, Programming, and Audiences in Greater China and the Chinese Diaspora |date = 2009-01-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|edition = First Edition |publisher = Palgrave Macmillan|isbn = 1403965781|pages = 205-236 |editors = Francoise Mengin (ed.)|last = Sum |first = Ngai-Ling|title = Cyber China: Reshaping National Identities in the Age of Information |chapter = Cyber-Capitalism and the Remaking of Greater China |location = Basingstoke|date = 2004-11-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|edition = 1|publisher = Palgrave |isbn = 1403965781|editors = Francoise Mengin (ed.)|last = Mengin |first = Francoise |title = Cyber China: Reshaping National Identities in the Age of Information |chapter = The Changing Role of the State in Greater China in the Age of Information |location = New York|date = 2004-11-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|volume = 8|issue = 4|pages = 81–102|last = Lee|first = C.C. |title = Rethinking political economy: Implications for media and democracy in Greater China|journal = JAVNOST-LJUBLJANA-|date = 2001}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last = William A. Callahan|title = Nationalism, Civilization and Transnational Relations: the discourse of Greater China |accessdate = 2007-12-14|url = http://www.informaworld.com/smpp/content~content=a713726334~db=all~order=page}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book| publisher = Palgrave Macmillan|isbn = 1403965781|pages = 71-90|editors = Francoise Mengin (ed.)|last = Hughes|first = Christopher|title = Cyber China: Reshaping National Identities in the Age of Information|chapter = Controlling the Internet Architecture Within Greater China |location = Basingstoke|date = 2004-11-24}}</ref>

大中華經濟圈，或稱經濟中國，指的是中國大陸、臺灣、港澳及世界的[[華人|華人]]企業家可以串連成立大中華經濟圈。台灣經濟學家[[鄭竹園|鄭竹園]]提出了「大中華共同市場」構想和「大中華經濟圈」概念。<ref name="He2001">{{cite book|author=Henry Yuhuai He|title=中华人民共和国政治文化用语大典|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=O6ac30QVU-4C&pg=PA48|accessdate=1 December 2012|year=2001|publisher=M.E. Sharpe|isbn=978-0-7656-0569-6|pages=48–}}</ref><ref name="中國大陸研究">{{cite book |title=中國大陸研究 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=4zE2AQAAIAAJ |accessdate=23 January 2013 |year=1999 |publisher=國立政治大學國際關係研究中心 |archive-date=2014-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922143726/http://books.google.com/books?id=4zE2AQAAIAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="鐘啟賓2007">{{cite book|author=鐘啟賓|title=搞懂規則,賺遍大陸: WTO下的兩岸經貿|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=K6bh7J8vxK0C&pg=PA246|accessdate=23 January 2013|year=2007|publisher=秀威資訊科技股份有限公司|isbn=978-986-6909-97-9|pages=246|archive-date=2014-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925211055/http://books.google.com/books?id=K6bh7J8vxK0C&pg=PA246|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="中華戰畧學刊">{{cite book|title=中華戰畧學刊|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XnhMAQAAIAAJ|accessdate=23 January 2013|year=2002|publisher=中華戰畧學會|archive-date=2014-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140930092230/http://books.google.com/books?id=XnhMAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="財團法人海峡交流基金會年報">{{cite book|title=財團法人海峡交流基金會年報|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=1HU3AQAAIAAJ|accessdate=23 January 2013|year=1997|publisher=財團法人海峡交流基金會|archive-date=2014-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925205020/http://books.google.com/books?id=1HU3AQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="鄭竹園">{{Cite web |url=http://ccheng.iweb.bsu.edu/Cheng20080629.pdf |title=Major Contributions (in Chinese) |access-date=2012-12-02 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125310/http://ccheng.iweb.bsu.edu/Cheng20080629.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://big5.huaxia.com/la/jwgc/00228941.html  “大中華經濟圈”勢不可擋 ] {{Wayback|url=http://big5.huaxia.com/la/jwgc/00228941.html |date=20210222201415 }}，華夏經緯網，08/05/2004</ref>大中華政治圈或稱政治中國相較之下較少被提及，可能和[[國共內戰|國共內戰]]歷史和[[臺灣統獨議題|臺灣統獨議題]]有關。<ref name="He2001"/>大中華文化圈則一般用以指同[[漢字文化圈|漢字文化圈]]所相近的一個文化區域，但日本及其他部分使用漢字的國家通常不屬於大中華文化圈所指代的範圍。

== 使用 ==
许多跨国公司使用“大中华”作为部门或分公司名称，如总部位于上海的[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]大中华部门<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2017/07/isabel-ge-mahe-named-apple-managing-director-of-greater-china/|title=Isabel Ge Mahe named Apple’s managing director of Greater China|author=|date=|work=|accessdate=2019-03-23|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203133010/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2017/07/isabel-ge-mahe-named-apple-managing-director-of-greater-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[麥肯錫公司|麥肯錫公司]]大中华部门<ref>{{Cite web|title=Greater China {{!}} McKinsey & Company|url=https://www.mckinsey.com/cn|accessdate=2020-01-18|work=www.mckinsey.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203132850/https://www.mckinsey.com/cn|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[寶潔公司|寶潔公司]]大中華部門<ref>{{Cite web|title=P&G in Greater China|url=https://www.pgcareers.com/location-greaterchina|accessdate=2020-01-18|work=www.pgcareers.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027003927/https://www.pgcareers.com/location-greaterchina|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[微软|微软]]大中华区<ref>{{cite web| title=柯睿杰接掌微软大中华区| url=https://news.microsoft.com/zh-cn/%E6%9F%AF%E7%9D%BF%E6%9D%B0%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%8C%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E5%8C%BA/| date=2016-07-04| author=Jiao, Tingting| website=微軟新聞中心| access-date=2020-09-22| archive-date=2021-02-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203132944/https://news.microsoft.com/zh-cn/%E6%9F%AF%E7%9D%BF%E6%9D%B0%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%8C%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E5%8C%BA/| dead-url=no}}</ref>等。學術研究中也有使用，如[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]的大中華研究所<ref>{{Cite web|title=Greater China|url=http://weai.columbia.edu/research/regions/china-region/|accessdate=2020-01-18|work=weai.columbia.edu|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807185712/http://weai.columbia.edu/research/regions/china-region/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[香港電台|香港電台]]開設有“透視大中華”-{zh:欄目;zh-hans:栏目;zh-hant:欄目;zh-tw:節目;}-，報道中國大陸、台灣及澳門新聞<ref>{{cite web |title=透視大中華 |url=https://podcast.rthk.hk/podcast/item.php?pid=907&lang=zh-CN |website=香港電台 |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222201503/https://podcast.rthk.hk/podcast/item.php?pid=907&lang=zh-CN |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但該詞語並非總是包含台灣，例如[[思科公司|思科公司]]提及相關地區時使用「大中華和台灣」<ref>{{cite web |title=The Rundown: Pegatron’s Tesla Ambitions, Tech Sector Bonuses, and Cisco’s New Software Center |url=https://topics.amcham.com.tw/2021/01/january-rundowns-business-w2/ |website=topics.amcham.com.tw |publisher=Taiwan Topics |access-date=18 January 2021 |quote=U.S. tech giant Cisco’s Managing Director for Greater China and Taiwan George Chen announced on January 13 that the company is set to open its first software center in the Asia-Pacific in Linkou after the Lunar New Year holiday. |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222201442/https://topics.amcham.com.tw/2021/01/january-rundowns-business-w2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在新闻与科学学术方面，“大中华地区”往往作为地域限制方式使用。

== 爭議 ==
[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]前[[外交部長|外交部長]][[吳學謙|吳學謙]]曾在1995年指出，該國政府反對「大中華經濟圈」这一概念，一些[[中华人民共和国政府|中华人民共和国政府]]領導人認為此詞將中國大陸和[[臺灣|臺灣]]同等對待。学者[[王赓武|王赓武]]質疑「大中華」一詞會有誤導或錯誤的效果，讓其他地域的國家質疑中華人民共和國傾向[[帝國主義|帝國主義]]擴張；他認為這詞絕不應該用在[[海外華人|海外華人]]，大中華在他看來是[[迷思|迷思]]，若將此詞延伸到中國大陸、[[香港|香港]]、臺灣[[兩岸三地|兩岸三地]]外之地方，這個詞將開始有誤導的政治效應，有不良效果。<ref name="He2001"/>

但该名词一直在经济领域被大量使用。尽管中国内地近年多次兴起对于涉中外资企业在境外没有严格贯彻[[一个中国|一个中国]]原则而产生的抵制运动，但是该用语并未受到强制监管和更正要求，依然作为经济领域的通行用语。

